author: zongaro
msg: Folding changes from the MAIN branch back into the XSLTC_DTM branch.

author: zongaro
msg: Fixed a bug with stack that was growing in SAXImpl.DOMBuilderImpl.linkParent
method, but from which elements were never popped.
Changed the SAXImpl.characters(int node, TransletOutputHandler) method to use
the output handler's character(String) method rather than converting the String
value of the TEXT node to a char[].
Also, cleaned up some indentation problems, removed some methods that were no
longer used and some code that was commented out.  (Still more to do, though!)

author: zongaro
msg: Changed code to use a merge sort with a sweep through after to eliminate
duplicates rather than using insertion sort.  The insertion sort performed
poorly when there were large numbers of unique nodes.
Might want to look at a synthesis of the two.

author: mkwan
msg: Update the extension samples to use the new namespace.
